parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of an impact, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The SRS light illuminates and stays on
the airbag warning light is on
the airbag system is inoperative
the airbag light resets multiple times.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: OPDS Sensor Failure (Occupant Position Detection System)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the OPDS sensor can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the deployment of airbags in non-crash situations or the failure to deploy airbags in crash situations.
symptoms: The SRS light illuminates and stays on
the airbag warning light is on
the OPDS sensor triggers SRS DTCs
the passenger side OPDS sensor is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Unavailable Recall Repairs (Airbag Recall)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of recall repairs can cause owners to continue driving vehicles with potentially faulty airbag systems, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The manufacturer exceeds a reasonable amount of time for recall repairs
parts are not available for recall repairs
the manufacturer fails to notify owners of recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates on its own
the engine rises up and takes off
the vehicle is difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or exhibit erratic shifting behavior, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle emits a loud noise
stalls
lacks power
has difficulty accelerating
skips gears
slips
or experiences early upshifts
especially between 40-60 mph.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The leakage of a corrosive and potentially toxic liquid from the rear view mirror can cause damage to the interior of the vehicle, including the instrument panel, steering wheel, and front seats, and may also cause skin irritation and health problems for the occupants.
symptoms: A gritty liquid secretes from the rear view mirror
splattering on the instrument panel
steering wheel
and front seats
and causing disintegration of the leather where it is not wiped away. The liquid may also cause skin irritation and health problems.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A defective rear window regulator can cause safety hazards while driving, including reduced visibility and potential accidents.
symptoms: The rear window regulator fails to function properly
causing issues with the rear window's operation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the navigation system can cause inconvenience and frustration for the driver, potentially leading to distractions while driving.
symptoms: The navigation system does not function properly
displays incorrect information
or freezes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag light can indicate a potential problem with the airbag system, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on
indicating a potential problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The flaking of paint and rusting of underlying metal can lead to structural damage and compromise the safety of the vehicle.
symptoms: Paint chips and flakes off
exposing underlying metal to rust
especially on the front
hood
roof
and sides of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to read important gauges and indicators on the instrument panel can lead to accidents or other safety issues.
symptoms: The instrument panel is not visible during daylight conditions
making it impossible to read mileage
see open door indicators
or access other important information.
